Amazon EC2 (Elastic Compute Cloud)
IaaS - Easily scalable - control over your cloud infrastructure
Integrates with tons of tools.

AWS Elastic Beanstalk
PaaS - load balancing and autoscaling

AWS CodeBuild - CI 
AWS CodeDeploy - CD 
AWS CodePipeline - full code pipeline from build to deploy
AWS CodeStar - integrates all parts of the process with management tools 
	and JIRA issue tracking

IaC (infra as code)
CloudFormation - Stack templating engine, YAML or Json based
OpsWorks - IaC with Chef

Serverless
AWS Lambda - run serverless functions 

Monitoring
Amazon Cloudwatch - track matrics and logs, set alarms and 
	automate responses to monitoring data


